title: A discussion of the agnostic side of UFO investigation
itunes:title: A discussion of the agnostic side of UFO investigation
description:
George Noory and Sarah Scoles discuss her work as a UFO researcher who does not use spirituality and religion in her work. They discuss alien abductions, UFO sightings and the difference between God and the Universe.
